and my kids.

02:37.505 --> 02:39.289
God, I just hired
an assistant.

02:39.333 --> 02:40.464
Here's your coffee,
Mr. Parker.

02:40.508 --> 02:41.987
Oh.
Thank you, Isabel.

02:42.031 --> 02:44.076
Time to fire her.
Everyone, really.

02:44.120 --> 02:45.252
