02:45.295 --> 02:46.601
Because you're the boss.

02:46.644 --> 02:47.689
T.G.I. Friday, bossman.

02:47.732 --> 02:48.994
Historically speaking,

02:49.038 --> 02:51.040
Friday is the best day
to fire people.

02:51.083 --> 02:53.347
Hey, boss.
Closed on the condo.

02:53.390 --> 02:54.348
Great.

02:54.391 --> 02:55.653
I just want
to thank you

02:55.697 --> 02:57.133
for convincing me
to pull the trigger.

02:57.177 --> 02:58.221
Okay.

02:58.265 --> 02:59.309
Okay.

02:59.353 --> 03:01.529
You know, uh...

03:01.572 --> 03:04.140
I-I feel like,
for the first time

03:04.184 --> 03:05.881
since I've lost my son,

03:05.924 --> 03:08.579
that everything's
coming up Shelly.

03:08.623 --> 03:09.493
[ Laughs ]

03:09.537 --> 03:10.668
Yeah.

03:10.712 --> 03:13.193
Okay, okay, okay.

03:13.236 --> 03:14.498
Okay.

03:15.586 --> 03:18.110
-You're gonna be fine.
-I don't want to be fine.

03:18.154 --> 03:20.548
