03:29.296 --> 03:30.601
Must be a sign!

03:30.645 --> 03:32.864
Why don't you all come on down,
kick back --

03:32.908 --> 03:34.953
Look, I appreciate the offer,
all right,

03:34.997 --> 03:37.434
