just the four of you?

05:28.197 --> 05:30.417
Yeah, that's --
How many do you guys have?

05:30.460 --> 05:32.070
Oh, I don't count miracles.

05:32.114 --> 05:33.985
But if I did,
they'd be them.

05:34.029 --> 05:35.987
[ Harmonizing ]

05:36.031 --> 05:38.947
♪ Jesus, Jesus

05:38.990 --> 05:40.383
They're all -- all yours?
All five?

05:40.427 --> 05:41.558
They seem so old.

05:41.602 --> 05:42.907
When did you start
having kids?

05:42.951 --> 05:44.561
Uh, we had Naomi
when I was 40.

05:44.605 --> 05:46.041
Uh, how old is she?

05:46.084 --> 05:47.782
She just had her 25th birthday.

05:47.825 --> 05:49.174
