Uh, you're 65?

05:49.218 --> 05:50.654
Yeah, yeah.

05:50.698 --> 05:52.264
Healthy living,
dose of vitamin and supplements,

05:52.308 --> 05:53.396
and three roots a day.

05:53.440 --> 05:54.615
Hey!

05:54.658 --> 05:56.051
Come on, love.

