of Heaven," yada yada yada?

06:35.133 --> 06:36.657
Oh, yeah. My mom said
heaven's a lie

06:36.700 --> 06:38.049
so people
don't get scared.

06:38.963 --> 06:40.791
-It's head down, mate.
